    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You stand firm against an attack.</p><p><em><strong>Range:</strong> Self (or 1 Space if wielding a Melee Weapon or Shield)</em></p><p><strong>Trigger:</strong> A target you can see within range (including yourself) is targeted by an Attack against its AD.</p><p><strong>Reaction:</strong> You grant the target a +5 bonus to its AD against this Attack.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Maneuver Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Targets: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>You can target 1 additional creature within range that’s also targeted by the same Attack.</p><p><strong>Grapple: (1 SP)</strong> If the Attacker is within 1 Space of you, they make a Physical Save. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The Attacker becomes Grappled by you once the Attack is resolved.</p>",
